Variable Beschreibung Beispiel <code>PROCESSWIRE_API_URL</code> Backend API URL (serverseitig) <code>https://www.bioco.ch/api</code> <code>NEXT_PUBLIC_PROCESSWIRE_API_URL</code> Backend API URL (clientseitig) <code>https://www.bioco.ch/api</code> <p>Konfiguration in <code>next.config.js</code>: <pre><code>env: {
  PROCESSWIRE_API_URL: process.env.PROCESSWIRE_API_URL || 'https://staging.bioco.ch/api',
}
</code></pre></p>
